## APACHE2
- /etc/apache2/sites-enabled
- sudo service apache2 restart

#### Apache Conf
```
<VirtualHost *:80>
	ServerName api.mycoin.store
 	ServerAlias api.mycoin.store
	ProxyRequests off

	<Proxy *>
		Order deny,allow
		Allow from all
	</Proxy>
        <Location />
		ProxyPass http://localhost:5000/
		ProxyPassReverse http://localhost:5000/
	</Location>
</VirtualHost>
```

